          <p class="lead-sub">A research pipeline from representation to intervention on complex networks.</p>

          <div class="research-flow" aria-label="Research pipeline">
            <div class="flow-step" data-flow="structure">
              <div class="flow-kicker">01</div>
              <h3>Structure</h3>
              <p>operators · representations · spectral views</p>
