              <h3>Interaction</h3>
              <p>coupled systems · cross-network effects</p>
              <div class="flow-support">e.g., <span class="map-chip map-chip-paper">AAAI 2024</span> <span class="map-chip map-chip-paper">WWW 2026</span> <span class="map-chip map-chip-paper">KDD 2025</span></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flow-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</div>
            <div class="flow-step" data-flow="uncertainty">
