            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="statement-copy compact-copy">
            <p>I study how structure, interaction, and uncertainty shape learning, inference, and decision-making across complex networks. My work combines spectral graph theory, machine learning, uncertainty quantification, and optimization to build models that are not only predictive, but also interpretable and transferable.</p>
